item.title: SekaiCTF 2024
item.description: SekaiCTF 2024 Description SekaiCTF is back for its third iteration! This year’s competition will feature various categories designed to test participants’ skills and incentivize learning. Our CTF will have more difficult challenges, and are catered towards intermediate and advanced players—however, there will still be beginner-friendly challenges to welcome players on the newer side.
